{"tid":813670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微信遭山寨！山寨微信比正版微信更多功能","createTime":"2018-09-10T15:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T03:13:19.000Z","uid":20058,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab6040439d6b33fc7671d42c6820038817ffb34","tid":813670,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/288669908528646/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F288669908528646%2F&d=ZjsqiCRAtuumaJOgmOTu9wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=40da6af4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/288669908528646/</a><br />\n<br />\n現在只要在網上搜尋「微信」，就會出現大量的山寨微信，售價介乎10至68元。他們聲稱可以在同一部手機上同時使用多個微信帳戶，而且內置自動搶紅包功能，可以防止對方撤回訊息，自設全球定位任何地方，還稱絕對不會被微信封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n記者下載了其中一個叫「魅影微商」的軟件來測試，安裝後微信的版面出現明顯改變，新增了許多功能，包括可以隨便更改步行量，可用來暪騙保險公司，令保費少一些。有學者指，當微信加上自動收錢和自設定位等功能，就很容易被不法分子利用。<br />\n<br />\n微信亦有留意到這些山寨外掛，指它們嚴重侵犯微信的著作權，又指這些外掛程式經常會留有後門及木馬具有嚴重的安全使用風險，將配合公安部門嚴厲打擊這類非法行為。"},{"pid":"f704c609bdc0bc05e6e48007c372f1df655c99b6","tid":813670,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeec10732040b947e3fca37f18d5df8883a1abc2","tid":813670,"uid":39550,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:43:03.000Z","msg":"dog bite dog <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3ca2063a6f283908a0b679f47a2d1c6936ad9f","tid":813670,"uid":5715,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:43:07.000Z","msg":"又指這些外掛程式經常會留有後門及木馬具有嚴重的安全使用風險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55bc347ae30d7c2f61053f773e4ade8021fdcf6","tid":81